    <title>想妳</title>
    <url>/2019/11/11/%E6%83%B3%E4%BD%A0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>我好想妳<br>我好想用力抱住妳<br>永远永远</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">螃蟹在剥我的壳，</span><br><span class="line">笔记本在写我，</span><br><span class="line">漫天的我落在枫叶上雪花上，</span><br><span class="line">而你在想我。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
